data.description: *SELLER OFFERING $5K AT CLOSING* Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled in the charming city of Port Richey. Boasting an array of attractive features, including abundant natural light and a refreshing pool, this residence offers a comfortable and inviting living experience. The spacious and thoughtfully designed floor plan encompasses three well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom, ensuring a peaceful retreat at the end of a long day. The additional bedrooms are versatile and can be easily transformed into home offices, guest rooms, or play areas to suit your specific needs.    Another notable feature of this property is its potential for generating revenue through short-term rentals. The popularity of Port Richey and the many surrounding towns as a tourist destination make this home an excellent investment opportunity. Whether you choose to use it as a primary residence, a vacation home, or an income-generating property, the versatility of this home presents a multitude of possibilities. The home is currently used as a short term rental with proven success.    Conveniently located near shopping, dining, entertainment, and within a short drive to the beautiful Gulf Coast beaches, this home offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning property your own and experience the best of Port Richey living. Schedule your showing today!    Notable updates include: Roof in 2020, Water Heater in 2018, Windows in 2017, Exterior Painted in 2021.
